The Pantheon Idea Graph

Once commits exist, artifacts form a history tree.

Example:

v0.1  ── commit ──> v0.2
  │
  └── branch → experimental_translation

This enables:
	•	experimental branches
	•	forks
	•	merges

Exactly like software development.

